cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with texture analysis and classification using computer vision and pattern recognition techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves feature extraction and classification, which are common topics in sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper involves image processing and analysis, which is a topic in cs.MM (Multimedia).
